Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.10,0:00:23.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}无止境的旅途中  止步不前之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:29.74,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}我们深深地叹气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}再次放开了紧握的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:44.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}但是现在已经没有什么可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:52.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}连接心灵之间那坚固的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:58.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}决不会被斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:07.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}继续寻求 终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:13.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在这个地方画上句号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}悲伤与愤怒 化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:28.02,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}命运就在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:30.78,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}本是没有交点的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:31.74,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:36.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}企图夺走我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:41.98,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使获得了想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么却
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:48.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}无法坦率地会心一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:53.74,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}流出的眼泪    不代表弱小或后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:58.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}只是孕育痛苦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:03.74,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不论什么样的瞬间与命运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:12.39,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终于明白了唯一可以确定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:15.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}极限也好  困难也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:19.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都不愿意放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:23.79,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就这样决不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:31.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紧握你的右手传来的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:35.98,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\blur2}就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你退到一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事 拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的脑子里出现 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金格·布拉德雷会冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我的东西做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强欲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个不知放弃 连过去都贪图的蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人和杰利姆少爷都没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警卫根本不是对手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙非常厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请隐居吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥莉薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得回家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你一下子说出这种没边际的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说把家主的位置让给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠闲地去清享余生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算让亚力士接我的班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让那种胆小鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把一切都托付给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后到外国去悠闲地休个假如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚力士只会给阿姆斯壮家的脸上抹黑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 您回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚力士 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奥莉薇战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把家主的位置让给赢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吧？奥莉薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我愿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥莉薇让我去别的地方隐居
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对父亲大人怎么这么无礼 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将全心全力使用全身的肌肉来做您的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆子不小 亚力士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就充分品尝自己的幼稚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 休假去哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清国如何 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说食物很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯萨琳也同意吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他们两人的特产怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大象怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又大又强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大象的话 我也想要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分出胜负了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮家的一切 由我接手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你最近和军队上层走得很近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个上层是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用自己的眼睛看 然后自己判断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了之后的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让父亲大人他们成为人质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们请去国外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,败者快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个房子是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是极东的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这前面只有沙漠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我接下来想回国
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回国？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 去清国
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越过沙漠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子一个人越过沙漠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 大伙 开始募集了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食物什么的都拿出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住一个晚上 明天再出发如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我家洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 史蒂文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那里房间很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她住下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好 我大女儿住过的房间正好空着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去中央都市上大学的艾米吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为你的女儿 还干得不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也得给这边的小猫点吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不是把你当成食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事吧 小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 说看起来很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是群好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要见死不救吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就算把我这半死不活的人造人带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也派不上什么用处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 去中央都市的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能找到真正长生不老的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的人也能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对马上要回国的你来说 都是没关系的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 谢谢你们的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有没做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你去了中央都市就是我的地盘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有贤者之石就能再变身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有石头的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前使用过的隐藏之处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弟弟在这里吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔的话 一定在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不是没人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是靠不住的大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从北方拚命逃到这里 结果却是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 古利德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子…饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是麟…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是老样子 吃太多了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急食物都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边是同伴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猩猩先生和…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是达律斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫亨克尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以前是军人 因为一些原因和这个小鬼一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么说明才好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是人造人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 这么轻易地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说的话就成为很长的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 为什么你会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古利德那家伙和人造人一伙断了关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我趁它那时候动摇的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取回了身体的主导权
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中央都市的附近寻找能够栖身的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古利德要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂—— 等——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 别输了 保持意识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中央都市地下的那个父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会在约定的日子打开门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为外行人的想法是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们兄弟跳进那里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩是不是都能恢复原来的身体呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开门需要通行费…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙为了什么打开门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定的日子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开门有特定的日子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是让你出来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把口信交给兰芳了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口信？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔交给她了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在不知道她在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 清国的皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滔滔不绝讲了那么多多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是古利德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省省吧 用这家伙可杀不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放过我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么放过不放过 刚才这家伙说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和人造人断了关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记忆混乱 袭击了布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去也不知道会被怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就这么逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算一个人随意生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能成为我们的同伴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有可去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴吗 那可真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上所有的东西都是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想成为我的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么和你一起去也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的体内明明有那么多灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 成为爱德他们的同伴就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不愿意 就把这个身体还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成为清国的皇帝之后来填补你的空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一国之王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺大的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼 太小了 太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拿的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就成为世界的王 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 麟 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太麻烦了 就古利麟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 谁是古利…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就成为你的手下吧 古利麟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说本大人成为你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等于跟着我的这些合成兽大叔也是你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小鬼 擅自做什么主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别得意过头了 你这个豆丁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小粒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想 在决定成为军队的走狗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 摇摇尾巴算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 任凭感情暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能失去机会和情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千载难逢的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么让感情暴走 失去贵重的情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为我的部下就是在影子下生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别后悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于后悔 我可以有自己的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了 那么你们也是部下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我们饭吃的话谁都行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺帅的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳环 一直寄放在我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时见不到温莉和阿尔了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定的日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,890)\fad(500,500)\3c&H000000&\blur4}达普利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 不要老过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会联系你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么频繁地过来 我都没法工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 卡迪斯精肉店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢光顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你预订的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也作为客人来光顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才军队的人来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从阿尔冯斯君和霍恩海姆那里获得的口信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,890)\fad(500,500)\3c&H000000&\blur4}北方之都近郊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是牵连很大的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定之日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,890)\fad(500,500)\3c&H000000&\blur4}布里克斯山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点联络本部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是P点 有袭击者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 是德拉古马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方的兵力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名？是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我问是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P点 是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是主妇…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,890)\fad(500,500)\3c&H000000&\blur4}布里克斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷之女袭击了山岳警备兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和20年前左右的事件相同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一个人全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果阿姆斯壮少将回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被杀了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,890)\fad(500,0)\3c&H000000&\blur4}同地·监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑眼镜 混血伊修瓦尔系和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫西干巨汉的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和听说的完全一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你们等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 是路过的主妇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带来了阿尔的口信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦喊退旁人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,890)\fad(500,0)\3c&H000000&\blur4}北方之都郊外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 是阿尔冯斯·艾尔利克的口信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是“约定之日”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？“约定之日”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,890)\fad(500,500)\3c&H000000&\blur4}东方之都·古拉曼官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 雷贝嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是老样子有一身好枪法 and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拉曼中将 你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战场上可不能让人有可乘之机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你和霍克爱中尉关系不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,890)\fad(500,0)\3c&H000000&\blur4}中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 雷贝嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方军和东方军的共同演习变更了计划
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:20:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为前阵子在布里克斯和德拉古马发生战斗的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改在东边搞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从大总统那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古大佐之后是大总统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也给我介绍几个中央都市的好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾风号 你的主人好冷血 小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要抓到好男人 完美退休
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给哈博克少尉问声好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给哈博克少尉问声好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体的状况安定之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备转移到东部医院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 会变得冷清了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道要拿些像样的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 礼物 一天一根哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢了 刚好抽完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷贝嘉也很担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐来的话 帮我问声好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是这么说的 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么好躲的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都在被人监视
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为私事过多接触而被怀疑就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服 大佐也抽一根吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说…就一根
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过完年的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方和东方都将行动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年后的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们的决意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年将思念放在胸口 朝着虎穴前进
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.41,0:24:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.04,0:24:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.69,0:24:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第46话 逼近的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使分离两地 心灵依然相通
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.96,0:24:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还在继续前进…
